properties.Name: ExperianConsumerCreditInquiry
properties.Description:
The date or dates when inquiries were initiated. 

Multiple dates may show if multiple inquiries were made by the same lender or organization.

Columns.Name: ExperianReportNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian consumer.

Columns.Name: InquiryDate
Columns.Description: The date or dates when inquiries were initiated. Multiple dates may show if multiple inquiries were made by the same lender or organization.

Columns.Name: AccountName
Columns.Description: Typically, accounts listed are the names of a lenders granting potential credit initiated by you. There are other organizations that may have a permissible purpose to access your credit.

Columns.Name: RemovalDate
Columns.Description: Inquiries are maintained for 2 years from the date of request.

Columns.Name: ContactStreetPoBox
Columns.Description:
The 'street/po box' component of the contact address.

This is the contact information provided by the creditor for this account. In some cases, there may only be an address available.

Columns.Name: ContactCity
Columns.Description:
The 'city' component of the contact address.

This is the contact information provided by the creditor for this account. In some cases, there may only be an address available.

Columns.Name: ContactState
Columns.Description:
The 'state' component of the contact address.

This is the contact information provided by the creditor for this account. In some cases, there may only be an address available.

Columns.Name: ContactTelephoneNumber
Columns.Description:
The contacts telephone number.

This is the contact information provided by the creditor for this account. In some cases, there may only be an address available.

Columns.Name: Comment
Columns.Description:
A comment regarding the credit inquiry.

Ex:
- Real estate loan on behalf of 3903 Merchants Express M.    This inquiry is scheduled to continue of record until 8-2014.

Columns.Name: ExperianCreditInquiryTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian Credit Inquiry Type.

Columns.Name: ExperianBusinessTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Experian business type.
